detaileddescription.para: Callback function used to free data from a list.

memberdef.definition: typedef int(* xmlListDataCompare)(const void *data0, const void *data1)
memberdef.name: xmlListDataCompare

detaileddescription.para: xmlListDataCompare: : the first data : the second data
Callback function used to compare 2 data.
Returns 0 is equality, -1 or 1 otherwise depending on the ordering.

memberdef.definition: typedef int(* xmlListWalker)(const void *data, const void *user)
memberdef.name: xmlListWalker

detaileddescription.para: xmlListWalker: : the data found in the list : extra user provided data to the walker
